Description: DEEPX Runtime Library
 DEEPX Runtime (DXRT) library for running neural network inference
 on DEEPX NPU hardware.
 This package contains the source code and build system. On installation,
 the C++ runtime library and Python (dx-engine) module are built and
 installed automatically. The build requires the dependencies listed above,
 matching the packages installed by install.sh --all (--dep + --onnxruntime).